{"tid":1400341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下無人機喺電纜鐵塔放低啲鐵線會否令全港大停電？","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:08:05.000Z","uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98af8ba79da7ec398b96898837bc69cabca0e1c8","tid":1400341,"uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"香港島嗰面啲架空電線係咪已經無電架啦 ?"},{"pid":"40e2d7186554a527ab00137465abb73bbf67a65c","tid":1400341,"uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hk-phy.org/energy/power/elect_phy/images/CLP_power_distribution1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk-phy.org%2Fenergy%2Fpower%2Felect_phy%2Fimages%2FCLP_power_distribution1.gif&h=2379b84c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bc5c398046cef5630791eaaae54865a375dcb7c","tid":1400341,"uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:23:53.000Z","msg":"我相信大家都有過停電的感受，非常煩躁。現在網絡時代，一停電，就沒有網絡，沒有空調、不能洗澡等，好難受。<br />\n<br />\n在現代社會，人們對電依賴與日俱增，也讓我們的世界變得特別脆弱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果在戰爭中摧毀敵方的供電網絡，足以令敵方不戰自潰，以及引起社會騷亂。科幻電影《地球停轉之日》中，外星人為了停止人類核武器競賽，而讓地球上所有電器停止工作1小時以示警告。<br />\n<br />\n而在現實生活中，1991年爆發的海灣戰爭，以美國為首的多國部隊發動了「沙漠風暴」行動空襲伊拉克，其中就使用了「石墨炸彈」 這種高科技武器。大量的石墨炸彈投向伊拉克的供電系統，使其全國大約85%的供電系統癱瘓，伊拉克在整個空襲中沒有任何還手之力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍BLU-114石墨炸彈可攻擊電網<br />\n1999年，北約對南聯盟的空襲中，美軍又使用了石墨炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n石墨炸彈在這兩場戰爭中的表現，讓科幻武器變為現實。<br />\n<br />\n那麼石墨炸彈到底是個什麼鬼？<br />\n<br />\n石墨纖維<br />\n石墨炸彈俗稱「軟炸彈」，其實就是在彈體中裝有石墨纖維絲，對人體沒有殺傷力。不過石墨是一種很好的導體，石墨炸彈中的石墨纖維絲屬於高純度的石墨，導電性能非常好，而且由於石墨纖維絲非常細，可以在空中長時間漂浮。"},{"pid":"5c65ebca4192d9bacd792f3b24c83b8e5ed87782","tid":1400341,"uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"解放軍裝備的國產500KG航空石墨炸彈<br />\n很多石墨纖維絲在空中組成一張網，如果飄落到高壓電線和變電設備，就會使整個電網短路從而癱瘓。石墨炸彈的這些性質，對敵方的電網系統有巨大的殺傷力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台軍雄風-2E導彈可搭載發射碳纖<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://i1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1000/s/i1.kknews.cc/SIG=qpe1nq/7sp0001pno8s9914224.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1000%2Fs%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3Dqpe1nq%2F7sp0001pno8s9914224.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=PwwdVKvQMhnOdjdmHJS5OdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=9a721d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i1-kknews-cc.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1000/s/i1.kknews.cc/SIG=qpe1nq/7sp0001pno8s9914224.jpg[img]</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.plo.vn/w653/Uploaded/2019/ovunjht/2017_10_10/blu-114-b-reformy-plo_buxr_thumb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.plo.vn%2Fw653%2FUploaded%2F2019%2Fovunjht%2F2017_10_10%2Fblu-114-b-reformy-plo_buxr_thumb.png&h=04f078c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b23454cb0aa2bdd98d64f0cd83dca1bb42909c72","tid":1400341,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港島嗰面啲架空電線係咪已經無電架啦 ?</blockquote><br />\nYes"},{"pid":"04e5f259ca1313890264decbaf7b133791b8857d","tid":1400341,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:46:13.000Z","msg":"搞完連自己友都冇電唔知點算 而人哋就完全冇影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabaaa13a1f068ced8018bf03f8a2fb39cc9a083","tid":1400341,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"影響會有<br />\n但後備發電機都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10402e50bc9c3975bd061ff7e138760ae74a8795","tid":1400341,"uid":255963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cabaaa13a1f068ced8018bf03f8a2fb39cc9a083","tid":1400341,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"影響會有<br />\n但後備發電機都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:08:05.000Z","msg":"你講緊嘅係 電力公司嘅後備發電 定係大廈/機構啲後備發電"}]}